episodes.title: Cart Crash with my Friend & Some Familiar JWs - Part 2
(40) Heaven & Earth, Spiritual & Physical - Conversations with a JW
episodes.description:
This is an interesting look at how the Watchtower skews its members' views of Scripture by its two class system teaching. It was hard to get a word in, as many times she cut me off and wouldn't even let me finish a full sentence, let alone a complete thought. 

#JW #heaven #earth
